{{#if (lte daysUntilExpiration 30)}}
<div class="alert-box alert-danger">
  <strong>üö® URGENT: Your HUBZone Certification is Expiring Soon!</strong>
</div>
{{else}}
<div class="alert-box alert-warning">
  <strong>‚è∞ HUBZone Certification Expiration Notice</strong>
</div>
{{/if}}

<h1>{{certificateType}} Expiration Notice</h1>

<p>Hi {{recipientName}},</p>

<p>This is a reminder that the HUBZone certification for <strong>{{businessName}}</strong> is approaching its expiration date.</p>

<div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
  <p style="font-size: 48px; margin: 0; line-height: 1;">
    {{#if (lte daysUntilExpiration 7)}}
    <span style="color: #ef4444;">{{daysUntilExpiration}}</span>
    {{else if (lte daysUntilExpiration 30)}}
    <span style="color: #f59e0b;">{{daysUntilExpiration}}</span>
    {{else}}
    <span style="color: #10b981;">{{daysUntilExpiration}}</span>
    {{/if}}
  </p>
  <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #6b7280; margin: 5px 0 0;">days until expiration</p>
  <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #9ca3af; margin: 10px 0 0;">
    Expires on: {{formatDate expirationDate}}
  </p>
</div>

<h2>Why Renewal Matters</h2>
<ul style="padding-left: 20px; color: #4b5563;">
  <li>Maintain your HUBZone set-aside contract eligibility</li>
  <li>Continue receiving price evaluation preferences</li>
  <li>Keep your HUBZone status for subcontracting opportunities</li>
  <li>Avoid gaps in certification that may affect ongoing contracts</li>
</ul>

<h2>How to Renew</h2>
<ol style="padding-left: 20px; color: #4b5563;">
  <li>Log in to your HZ Navigator dashboard</li>
  <li>Review and update your business information</li>
  <li>Verify employee residency documentation</li>
  <li>Submit your recertification application</li>
</ol>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
  <a href="{{renewalUrl}}" class="btn {{#if (lte daysUntilExpiration 30)}}btn-danger{{else}}btn-warning{{/if}}">
    Start Renewal Process
  </a>
</p>

<hr class="divider">

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
  Need assistance with your renewal? Our support team is ready to help. Contact us at 
  <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #0073c7;">{{supportEmail}}</a>
</p>

